{"tid":197013,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖）海膽飯食評#1 銅鑼灣.Superdon","createTime":"2017-04-11T15:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T04:44:01.000Z","uid":215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffecba3c84b1e8ea8476e973c033bf62beb2b2c","tid":197013,"uid":215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"自己本身鍾意食海膽<br />\n見到隔離鋪插得咁勁 一於落去試吓<br />\n<br />\n比番張實物圖先 <br />\n 快手認得差<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3C2MUb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3C2MUb.jpg&h=c3f0b6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單計埋＋1 <br />\nhkd295一碗<br />\n你落單嗰陣佢會問你加唔加＄20<br />\n有碗湯同個沙律<br />\n我自己就唔加。因為已經漏到仆街<br />\n<br />\n海膽味道好鮮甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拖羅個樣係好睇<br />\n食落去唔香 油都唔夠多<br />\n同埋碗野有啲死人配菜<br />\n搞到唔係好襯<br />\n<br />\n咁啱坐吧枱<br />\n睇住佢哋切魚生<br />\n佢哋係冇帶手套嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個價錢有咁嘅份量 而且海膽好味<br />\n已經收貨<br />\n<br />\n當日我去到冇晒全海膽<br />\n所以先試左呢個<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n如果爛咀老細你見到我個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想同你講book位<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街。仲有一張到我<br />\n你自己個friend 帶住條女就走左入去<br />\n你叫佢哋入去嗰陣仲要講<br />\n&quot;Booking&quot;既呢一邊<br />\n唔緊要 fd底我唔怪你<br />\n當我黑仔<br />\n完"},{"pid":"74cd0c92f959ef6fea0d5e8431bb0da6d4e63d39","tid":197013,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"成三舊水一碗<br />\n<br />\n我都想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610b8c41bc8a292a82d1f3288a3cc98d43a25bb3","tid":197013,"uid":215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成三舊水一碗<br />\n<br />\n我都想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食海膽其實已經差唔多啦<br />\n有時啲嘢一分錢一分貨"},{"pid":"a85a65a735799ecc4a4459210faff99d1c86be24","tid":197013,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"295好似食定食doraya仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9af814bb330be364247afc63c6834df4b913f1c","tid":197013,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"定食doraya 自選海膽加其他料都唔洗295好似<br />\n<br />\n又跟前菜同湯"},{"pid":"2b2916e833a1ef5a1d29700f9b34662b61c470f0","tid":197013,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"3舊水得丁屎海膽"},{"pid":"5903fd138fae25626b669251c22c9732b6cb6618","tid":197013,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:29:28.000Z","msg":"$300食碗咁細 海膽仲要得咁小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e3399a58d2278883f83d494b6994af10c07d81","tid":197013,"uid":215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"我標準因為佢好食所以先覺得值<br />\n而且見你哋介紹嗰間似加拿大嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n唔理咁多下次試吓doraya <br />\n食完開返個post"},{"pid":"d178be6c68eb6320e925272143daa2010130bc59","tid":197013,"uid":215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>295好似食定食doraya仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見到openrice d相有北海道膽<br />\n嗰度要幾錢到"},{"pid":"5bc15d8d4642cfa5d6ab4f7232ad37ced720c0b0","tid":197013,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"自己買板靚海膽食唔好"},{"pid":"19eb3c49c55fc3603dc8af6fcc5acd92578c039c","tid":197013,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:20:49.000Z","msg":"啲料少到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9acaebf0420a5a0971bc2e0872672a6466cf74","tid":197013,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http